To run application inside VM with vagrant
=======================================

cd vagrant/
#...See vagrant/README


Setup framework for application
=================================

Install Java JDK --  sudo apt-get install openjdk-7-jdk -y 
Install sbt: http://www.scala-sbt.org/release/docs/Getting-Started/Setup.html
Download and unzip play framework: http://www.playframework.com/download
Add play framework to PATH (export PATH:$PATH:/home/user/play-2.2.1)


	Debian:

	mkdir ~/play 
	cd ~/play
	sudo apt-get install openjdk-7-jdk -y
	wget https://downloads.typesafe.com/play/2.2.1/play-2.2.1.zip
	unzip play-2.2.1.zip
	echo 'export PATH=$PATH:'$HOME'/play-2.2.1/play-2.2.1' >> ~/.bashrc
	source ~/.bashrc
	#Cleanup
	rm play-2.2.1.zip


Running application:
> cd BeamstreamPlay
> play run

Running application with development.conf:
>  play -Dconfig.file=conf/development.conf run
